1 C. The provisions of subsection A of this section shall not
2 apply to shipping charges, but if there are shipping charges, such
3 charges shall be clearly stated as a separate item.
4 D. The vendor shall provide the information to the buyer within
5 a reasonable period of time prior to payment for the goods or
6 services.
7 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
